# Homebrew Tap for carbon2cocoa

This tap contains the Homebrew formula for [carbon2cocoa](https://github.com/pascalharris/carbon2cocoa),
a tool to convert legacy Carbon XIB/NIB files to modern Cocoa format.

## Installation

```bash
brew tap pascalharris/carbon2cocoa
brew install carbon2cocoa
```

Or install directly:

```bash
brew install pascalharris/carbon2cocoa/carbon2cocoa
```

## Usage

```bash
carbon2cocoa input.xib           # Convert XIB file
carbon2cocoa input.nib           # Convert NIB package
carbon2cocoa --help              # Show help
```

## More Information

- [carbon2cocoa on GitHub](https://github.com/pascalharris/carbon2cocoa)
- [Manual page](https://github.com/pascalharris/carbon2cocoa/blob/main/carbon2cocoa.1)
